data.description: Welcome Home! Located in the GATED community, The Park at Rivers Edge, and built in 2019, you will love this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome with upstairs FLEX SPACE and attached GARAGE! The home features a spacious and open-concept floorpan with beautiful GRANITE countertops in the kitchen and baths as well as ceramic tile floors in all wet rooms. You will love the large primary bedroom with en-suite double vanity sinks and WALK-IN CLOSET!  Move-in ready with washer & dryer, a high tech fridge and stainless appliances. Enjoy cookouts with friends on your covered back patio in your private, FENCED-IN BACK YARD!The central location can't be beat. Just minutes to downtown Charleston, the Air Force Base, Bosch, Boeing, Trident Tech and the airport. And close to numerous shopping,dining and entertainment options too! Come see this gem today!
